The '''General National Hockey Federation''' or '''Libyan Hockey Federation''' is the [[sports governing body|governing body]] of [[Field hockey|Field Hockey]] in [[Libya]], [[Africa]]. Its Headquarters are in [[Tripoli]], Libya.It is affiliated to IHF [[International Hockey Federation]] and AHF [[African Hockey Federation]].

Salah Abdussalam Mhanni is the President of Hockey Association of Libya and Haitem Mohammed Saleem is performing the responsibilities of the General Secretary.<ref>{{cite news| url = http://www.fih.ch/inside-fih/our-members/libyahf/ | title = Libyan Hockey Federation - Information | work = FIH | access-date= 11 September 2017}}</ref>

